snippet.title: Astro Chase [Atari 800 Longplay] (1983) Parker Brothers
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the Atari 8-bit game Astro Chase. Released back in 1982 by First Star Software and then rereleased by Parker Brothers in 1983. Very good action space-themed parallax scrolling arcade quality game.
